{"tid":1550852,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國無興趣睇你地討論左膠同割蓆","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T02:30:42.000Z","uid":2617,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"1bea8cfe8f78566c9c623ffd77f510a5d52b3719","tid":1550852,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:06:54.000Z","msg":"各位手足 <br />\n美國國會就黎討論「香港民主及人權法案」<br />\n過唔過到 其中一個關鍵就係我地既訊息能否有效傳達比佢地<br />\n而我地要做既野就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日中午出黎集會遊行</span></span> <br />\n同埋 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不停做文宣傳出外國</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DfiB0aF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfiB0aF.jpg&h=547be3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家唔係討論咩左唔左膠同割唔割蓆<br />\n美國國會唔會理你呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地要見到既係你地表達<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強而有力既信息</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該聽日全部出去集會</span></span><br />\n話知你咩勇武和理非左膠鍵戰<br />\n有時間就睇多一次呢篇介紹法案既文章<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598-%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=4ae62ceb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598-%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&h=556f1be4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果美國國會見到你地FOCUS既係左膠同割蓆<br />\n佢地心入面都忍唔住笑 仲點會幫香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日1點半遮打見<br />\n2點半遊行開始<br />\n勇武和理 同 五大訴求<br />\n都係缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"249da6be49c5d775509086abbbcad383b214bcfe","tid":1550852,"uid":160247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"1777d737986e86806627680919b0febfe278e8b3","tid":1550852,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63a6c8675f79a984c8c2a1ccaa74d88ba386390d","tid":1550852,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"聽日1點半遮打見<br />\n2點半遊行開始<br />\n勇武和理 同 五大訴求<br />\n都係缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n追究612 721 811 831黑警暴行"},{"pid":"de374b75c9eb21777594238bfbc584a8314fe226","tid":1550852,"uid":221205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d7fa96b0125384353305c8c33f5e9f255c4e3f2","tid":1550852,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:08:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":